[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:29,460 --> 00:01:34,979
[One and Only]

3
00:01:34,979 --> 00:01:37,979
[Episode 5]

4
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,530
Why did you pour the tea?

5
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:51,600
Follow me.

6
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,200
Master.

7
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,960
Why don't you allow Eleven to go enjoy the music?

8
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:25,360
It's rare to hear the music played by musicians from Nanxiao.

9
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,540
She poured a pot of tea.

10
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:32,650
I'm punishing her by asking her to copy tea names.

11
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:42,360
Master.

12
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:45,079
Are you teasing her

13
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,760
because she can't speak?

14
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,200
Famous tea is expensive.

15
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,720
But she wasted it at will.

16
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:52,410
Shouldn't she be punished?

17
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,930
Do you feel grieved?

18
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:22,360
You should know the value of a cup of tea

19
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,840
worth days of,

20
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:26,250
even a month of food for common people.

21
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,800
You like to drink tea.

22
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:28,980
So I bought you tea.

23
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,260
But I don't want you to be arrogant

24
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:34,180
and unaware of how hard common people's life is.

25
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,360
You should cultivate virtue by staying thrift.

26
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,000
You are the future Crown Princess.

27
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,460
You should set an example.

28
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,280
What's wrong?

29
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,600
As the Junior Prince of Nanchen's disciple,

30
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:04,860
I should remember it, but it has nothing to do with the name of Crown Princess.

31
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,920
I'm willing to be punished.

32
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,460
Most of the tea comes from Nanxiao

33
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,020
and the Jiduo Kingdom.

34
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,920
I handled that from Jiduo.

35
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,330
Wait. Let me find it out.

36
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,250
This one.

37
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,920
Yes, that's it.

38
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,880
Look, there're words on it.

39
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,120
Abstruse writing.

40
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:49,120
But it says cinnamon.

41
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,560
Cinnamon is not tea?

42
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:55,120
Then where's the tea?

43
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,780
When did you learn Jiduo's language?

44
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:06,320
When I went to the temple

45
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,960
to pray for you these two years,

46
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:09,080
I met monks from

47
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:09,720
the Jiduo Kingdom

48
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,920
and I learned it from them.

49
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,760
Since you can learn their language,

50
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:15,090
you must go to the temple very frequently.

51
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:17,450
I would go there when I miss you all.

52
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,920
No wonder Xie Yun always became wordy

53
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,240
when he went to the battlefield.

54
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,880
He said there was a little sister

55
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:24,840
waiting for us at home

56
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:26,640
and we should not lose our lives.

57
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,600
He knows you best.

58
00:05:31,660 --> 00:05:34,620
[Nanchen Royal Mansion]

59
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,440
The four of them are guards from the imperial palace.

60
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,900
They follow to protect me.

61
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,680
Zhou Tianxing.

62
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:48,760
Feng Qiao.

63
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,490
Greetings, Your Highness.

64
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,080
I know you.

65
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,960
You are a meritorious general following the Junior Prince of Nanchen

66
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:57,290
to suppress the Six-garrison Rebellion.

67
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,800
Where is my uncle?

68
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:01,720
Master is in the camp.

69
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,850
He left us to entertain Your Highness.

70
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,720
Uncle really loves soldiers as if they were his children.

71
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,000
It seems he is going to spend

72
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,600
the New Year's Eve with generals and soldiers.

73
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:20,120
Is there any scenic place

74
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,360
in his mansion?

75
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,800
I don't want her

76
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:29,480
to feel chained when we meet for the first time.

77
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,720
There is a garden

78
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,320
with pavilion, pond and beautiful scenery.

79
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:34,650
Shiyi often practices instrument there.

80
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:36,900
Then I'll go there.

81
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:54,560
People in the mansion

82
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,880
are talking about the Prince of Guangling.

83
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,400
They said he has been good-looking since he was a child

84
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:58,600
and he is famous outside the palace.

85
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,880
What they said is true.

86
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,440
He is a quite handsome man.

87
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:05,810
Why should we judge people by appearance?

88
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:09,360
Well, being good-looking is definitely not a disadvantage.

89
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,160
A hundred years ago, the emperor of Xiyan Kingdom,

90
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,040
Murong Chong,

91
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,400
was imprisoned as a toy-boy and suffered humiliation

92
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:16,000
when he was young

93
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,080
because he looked even better than women.

94
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:20,280
Isn't it all because of his appearance?

95
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,360
It was really a pity for you

96
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,420
to lose ability to speak these years.

97
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,520
No matter if he is your future husband

98
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,720
or just a guest from afar,

99
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,560
you should show hospitality.

100
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:37,640
You are more like the descendant from the Cui family than I am.

101
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,520
How I wish

102
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:40,840
you were me.

103
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,960
Greetings, Your Highness.

104
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:58,660
Your Highness.

105
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,360
We're not in the Central State.

106
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,520
No need to be too polite.

107
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,240
Get up.

108
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,620
Thank you, Your Highness.

109
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,280
I finally don't need to

110
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,740
see you through portrait.

111
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,960
In the Central State, I often heard that

112
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,880
Nanchen Royal Mansion is magnificent.

113
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,540
But I didn't take it seriouly.

114
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,920
Now that I'm here,

115
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,360
I realize it is true.

116
00:09:40,540 --> 00:09:43,070
Your Highness, don't be misled by the public.

117
00:09:43,220 --> 00:09:44,020
For what?

118
00:09:45,420 --> 00:09:47,500
My master is not extravagant.

119
00:09:48,220 --> 00:09:50,220
But as the prince guarding the borders,

120
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:52,100
his residence must be magnificent

121
00:09:52,100 --> 00:09:53,830
to win the hearts of the people.

122
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:55,860
You are afraid that I will think

123
00:09:55,860 --> 00:09:57,790
he is disloyal like other princes?

124
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:59,300
I dare not think so.

125
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:03,540
I'm not that blind and stupid.

126
00:10:04,020 --> 00:10:05,660
Other royal families and fierce generals

127
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:06,740
might be rebellious

128
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:08,020
or wait for an opportunity

129
00:10:08,020 --> 00:10:09,380
to rebel

130
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:10,580
when they take control of

131
00:10:10,580 --> 00:10:12,380
thousands of military soldiers.

132
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:14,220
But he won't.

133
00:10:14,460 --> 00:10:16,980
Beichen is so lucky to have him.

134
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,650
It's against the rules.

135
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,000
Are you all right?

136
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:34,970
I'm fine.

137
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:37,340
I'm just caring about you.

138
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,400
Show me your hand.

139
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:39,920
There are doctors in the mansion.

140
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:41,250
I'll see them by myself.

141
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:49,760
Send an imperial doctor to check her hand.

142
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:50,480
Now!

143
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:51,360
Yes.

144
00:11:02,820 --> 00:11:04,540
Why did you get hurt for the first time you met him?

145
00:11:04,540 --> 00:11:06,340
Is it an arrangement of the fate?

146
00:11:07,060 --> 00:11:08,700
He was closely surrounded by

147
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:10,020
four guards with knives.

148
00:11:10,020 --> 00:11:11,820
Even after the maids and chamberlains had left,

149
00:11:11,820 --> 00:11:13,080
they guarded him also.

150
00:11:13,420 --> 00:11:14,780
Is he afraid there would be

151
00:11:14,780 --> 00:11:17,110
assassins even in Nanchen Royal Mansion?

152
00:11:17,540 --> 00:11:19,000
That's the strange point.

153
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:28,860
Your Highness.

154
00:11:28,860 --> 00:11:29,580
How is she?

155
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:32,150
Miss Cui is all right. Don't worry.

156
00:11:34,580 --> 00:11:35,780
As soon as I saw her...

157
00:11:40,780 --> 00:11:42,220
I had a mood

158
00:11:42,380 --> 00:11:43,780
that I won't understand.

159
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:46,780
Although I have been castrated,

160
00:11:47,060 --> 00:11:48,140
I'm still a human.

161
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:51,460
Since I'm human, I have emotions.

162
00:11:55,580 --> 00:11:57,980
She is different from that on the portrait.

163
00:11:58,140 --> 00:12:00,470
She won't stand still to let me gaze at her.

164
00:12:05,780 --> 00:12:06,780
She will be afraid

165
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:09,020
and then get away from me.

166
00:12:12,300 --> 00:12:13,830
Uncle is not in the mansion.

167
00:12:14,260 --> 00:12:16,420
I have to find a good reason to see him.

168
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:31,030
Today is your birthday.

169
00:12:31,140 --> 00:12:32,140
What's your wish?

170
00:12:36,460 --> 00:12:39,020
Let me tell you what gifts I've prepared for you.

171
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:40,300
Your Highness is a guest.

172
00:12:40,300 --> 00:12:41,830
No need to spend money on me.

173
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:46,140
Greetings, Your Highness.

174
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:47,870
You two generals finally came.

175
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:50,240
Thank you, Your Highness.

176
00:12:50,940 --> 00:12:53,000
Your Highness, what can we do for you?

177
00:12:53,340 --> 00:12:54,820
I've prepared good wine and food.

178
00:12:54,820 --> 00:12:56,700
I want to go to the army barracks with you

179
00:12:56,700 --> 00:12:58,500
to celebrate Shiyi's birthday.

180
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:05,500
It feels like home in the royal mansion.

181
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:06,700
I think

182
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:11,500
Shiyi must want to celebrate her birthday

183
00:13:11,500 --> 00:13:12,580
with her family.

184
00:13:12,900 --> 00:13:14,500
But the Royal Army has strict rules.

185
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:16,180
Outsiders are not allowed to enter the camp without permission.

186
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:17,300
Am I an outsider?

187
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:20,630
I mean those without military status.

188
00:13:24,100 --> 00:13:25,700
What if I have an imperial edict

189
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:28,100
to reward the army on behalf of His Majesty?

190
00:13:34,780 --> 00:13:35,620
In this case,

191
00:13:35,940 --> 00:13:37,940
I'll make an arrangement right now.

192
00:13:48,060 --> 00:13:50,520
I just wanted to give you a birthday present.

193
00:13:51,860 --> 00:13:53,500
I didn't know you have an edict.

194
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:55,740
I'm sorry for embarrassing you.

195
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:57,800
Never mind.

196
00:13:58,340 --> 00:13:59,870
It's okay because it is you.

197
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:16,120
Your Highness.

198
00:14:16,420 --> 00:14:18,680
The poison has been completely cleared.

199
00:14:22,740 --> 00:14:23,340
Master.

200
00:14:24,140 --> 00:14:25,140
Eleven came.

201
00:14:26,620 --> 00:14:28,020
Isn't she in the mansion?

202
00:14:28,820 --> 00:14:30,540
The Prince of Guangling brought her here.

203
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:32,500
He said he wanted to hold a birthday party for her

204
00:14:32,500 --> 00:14:33,420
and took this opportunity

205
00:14:33,420 --> 00:14:35,820
to reward the army on behalf of His Majesty.

206
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:39,400
Let's go and welcome them.

207
00:14:42,460 --> 00:14:43,060
Uncle.

208
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:44,980
Zixing.

209
00:14:51,060 --> 00:14:51,990
Are you injured?

210
00:14:54,980 --> 00:14:57,640
Xie Yun, take Eleven to see the military doctor.

211
00:14:57,700 --> 00:14:58,220
Yes.

212
00:15:06,860 --> 00:15:07,540
Zixing.

213
00:15:07,780 --> 00:15:09,110
Take a break in the tent.

214
00:15:09,300 --> 00:15:09,860
No hurry.

215
00:15:10,420 --> 00:15:13,060
It's a rare opportunity for me to enter the army barracks.

216
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:14,580
I wonder if you are free

217
00:15:14,740 --> 00:15:15,860
to show me around.

218
00:15:17,180 --> 00:15:17,780
All right.

219
00:15:18,380 --> 00:15:19,110
Come with me.

220
00:15:26,710 --> 00:15:27,740
Show me your hand.

221
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,680
Master would be worried

222
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:33,100
if the military doctor didn't check your hand.

223
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:33,940
Although imperial doctors

224
00:15:33,940 --> 00:15:36,060
have high official titles and read a lot,

225
00:15:36,060 --> 00:15:37,790
they have less experience than

226
00:15:37,900 --> 00:15:39,220
our military doctors.

227
00:15:40,340 --> 00:15:41,420
I'm flattered.

228
00:15:43,380 --> 00:15:44,580
They have already used

229
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:46,060
good medicine for treating wound.

230
00:15:46,060 --> 00:15:47,620
But I have

231
00:15:47,620 --> 00:15:48,740
folk prescription

232
00:15:49,420 --> 00:15:51,420
which is better than this medicine.

233
00:15:51,660 --> 00:15:52,920
I'll get it right away.

234
00:16:01,140 --> 00:16:02,300
How did he treat you?

235
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:06,600
With courtesy and integrity.

236
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:08,140
You are shy.

237
00:16:10,020 --> 00:16:11,350
I've brought Tusu Wine.

238
00:16:12,820 --> 00:16:13,420
Okay.

239
00:16:14,020 --> 00:16:15,550
Since you don't want to say,

240
00:16:15,820 --> 00:16:16,950
forget my question.

241
00:16:22,500 --> 00:16:23,860
Be careful.

242
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:24,740
Place everything well.

243
00:16:24,740 --> 00:16:25,100
Yes.

244
00:16:25,220 --> 00:16:25,540
Yes.

245
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:30,360
It smells good.

246
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:34,430
It's all your favorite dishes.

247
00:16:38,540 --> 00:16:40,260
Master, I've brought Tusu.

248
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:42,220
Tusu?

249
00:16:43,980 --> 00:16:44,980
Dinner prepared tonight

250
00:16:44,980 --> 00:16:46,310
looks a little shabbier

251
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:48,260
compared with Tusu, Xie Yun.

252
00:16:49,540 --> 00:16:50,940
I'll kill some fat sheep.

253
00:16:51,900 --> 00:16:52,760
Give me a knife.

254
00:16:53,340 --> 00:16:54,020
Here.

255
00:17:07,819 --> 00:17:08,859
This cup of Tusu

256
00:17:09,420 --> 00:17:10,880
is for our guest from afar,

257
00:17:11,900 --> 00:17:12,540
Zixing.

258
00:17:16,380 --> 00:17:17,380
Thank you, Uncle.

259
00:17:18,540 --> 00:17:20,000
I also take this cup of wine

260
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:22,780
as a toast to all of you on behalf of His Majesty.

261
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:24,980
With a general who can win every battle,

262
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:27,710
the emperor doesn't have to build the Great Wall.

263
00:17:32,100 --> 00:17:33,540
Thank you, Your Majesty.

264
00:17:33,540 --> 00:17:35,140
Thank you, Your Highness.

265
00:18:02,020 --> 00:18:04,380
This toast is for

266
00:18:04,420 --> 00:18:05,660
the generals and soldiers

267
00:18:05,660 --> 00:18:08,260
who sacrificed in the rebellion suppression.

268
00:18:29,140 --> 00:18:30,620
Let's celebrate the New Year.

269
00:18:30,620 --> 00:18:31,750
I hope there would be

270
00:18:31,940 --> 00:18:33,670
no flames of war in our country.

271
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:36,460
May the people of Beichen live and work in peace and contentment.

