00:18:45,820 --> 00:18:47,260
enjoy prosperity.

277
00:19:00,220 --> 00:19:01,180
[Tusu Wine]

278
00:19:03,100 --> 00:19:05,340
Finally, I want to say that

279
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:09,540
today's Eleven's birthday.

280
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:11,300
I hope

281
00:19:11,300 --> 00:19:13,160
she could be happy every day here.

282
00:19:18,360 --> 00:19:18,960
Eleven.

283
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:20,850
