Who's inside?

571
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:41,860
It's His Highness.

572
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:44,960
He used to come to light a fire

573
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:46,000
before a war.

574
00:36:46,040 --> 00:36:46,840
But I've never

575
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:50,220
heard of an expedition this time.

576
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:57,240
Go get my reed flute.

577
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:58,240
Yes.

578
00:37:09,120 --> 00:37:10,520
I aroused your interest?

579
00:37:17,480 --> 00:37:18,840
No one in Shouyang understands me.

580
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:19,760
It's a rare opportunity to come back.

581
00:37:19,760 --> 00:37:21,360
I want to play a song with you.

582
00:37:21,520 --> 00:37:22,080
Okay.

583
00:37:22,520 --> 00:37:24,850
Our first Confucian general in Shouyang.

584
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,960
Who said this?

585
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:29,490
Who do you think would say this?

586
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:32,210
It must be General Hong.

587
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:10,760
You are awake.

588
00:38:11,200 --> 00:38:11,920
Xiaoyu.

589
00:38:12,520 --> 00:38:13,680
Who plays the music?

590
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:16,050
Master likes to play music before war.

591
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:19,000
It's rare that he plays music not for war

592
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:21,220
but for pleasing himself.

593
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:45,600
Master.

594
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:48,720
General Hong.

595
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:51,040
You got up late today.

596
00:38:53,040 --> 00:38:54,240
It's Eleven's fault.

597
00:38:56,220 --> 00:38:57,680
Then I'll leave her to you.

598
00:38:58,060 --> 00:38:58,940
In this camp,

599
00:38:58,940 --> 00:39:00,340
only you two are idle.

600
00:39:01,180 --> 00:39:02,840
Then I'll train the soldiers.

601
00:39:04,420 --> 00:39:05,380
I'm idle?

602
00:39:06,860 --> 00:39:07,720
Scouting camp.

603
00:39:08,300 --> 00:39:09,140
Military training.

604
00:39:09,140 --> 00:39:09,700
Yes.

605
00:39:11,140 --> 00:39:12,540
How did you two take the swords?

606
00:39:12,540 --> 00:39:13,420
Take them well.

607
00:39:14,860 --> 00:39:15,420
Line up.

608
00:39:15,620 --> 00:39:16,100
Yes.

609
00:39:19,860 --> 00:39:21,660
They seem to be afraid of Xiaoyu.

610
00:39:22,780 --> 00:39:23,740
In the barracks,

611
00:39:24,100 --> 00:39:25,100
it's much harder for a female general

612
00:39:25,100 --> 00:39:26,300
to convince soldiers

613
00:39:27,140 --> 00:39:28,470
than the male generals.

614
00:39:33,980 --> 00:39:34,820
I'm sorry for

615
00:39:36,700 --> 00:39:38,430
losing my courtesy last night.

616
00:39:39,540 --> 00:39:40,200
Never mind.

617
00:39:42,500 --> 00:39:43,820
Let me show you around

618
00:39:44,180 --> 00:39:44,980
the barracks.

619
00:39:52,540 --> 00:39:53,780
Pay attention to the action.

620
00:39:53,780 --> 00:39:55,440
When the army comes to a place,

621
00:39:55,620 --> 00:39:57,140
Xiaoyu's scouting camp

622
00:39:57,340 --> 00:39:59,340
will choose a place for the army to be stationed.

623
00:39:59,340 --> 00:40:02,400
The infantry will cut down trees and build wooden walls

624
00:40:02,540 --> 00:40:03,870
to form a military camp.

625
00:40:04,300 --> 00:40:06,960
Tighten your thighs and clamp the horse's back.

626
00:40:13,500 --> 00:40:14,620
Stop shivering.

627
00:40:19,340 --> 00:40:20,740
Look at you.

628
00:40:20,740 --> 00:40:21,340
Get up.

629
00:40:22,580 --> 00:40:23,140
Yes.

630
00:40:24,060 --> 00:40:26,390
Why are there wooden horses in the stable?

631
00:40:27,060 --> 00:40:28,260
It's much more expensive to raise a war horse

632
00:40:28,260 --> 00:40:29,820
than raising a soldier.

633
00:40:30,020 --> 00:40:31,620
So when they train at ordinary times,

634
00:40:31,620 --> 00:40:33,020
they all use fake horses.

635
00:40:34,060 --> 00:40:35,020
Xiaoyu said

636
00:40:35,340 --> 00:40:37,220
our country conquers land with cavalry.

637
00:40:37,220 --> 00:40:39,080
War horses are the most precious.

638
00:40:41,340 --> 00:40:41,940
Continue.

639
00:40:47,900 --> 00:40:49,300
I'll eat if you don't eat.

640
00:41:03,220 --> 00:41:03,900
Master.

641
00:41:08,700 --> 00:41:09,300
What is it?

642
00:41:09,660 --> 00:41:10,990
You don't like the food?

643
00:41:11,900 --> 00:41:12,300
I…

644
00:41:12,300 --> 00:41:13,820
He's still that ungrateful, just like how he was

645
00:41:13,820 --> 00:41:15,880
in the Buddhist Tower of the Mansion.

646
00:41:16,020 --> 00:41:16,620
Don't you

647
00:41:16,620 --> 00:41:17,780
underestimate him.

648
00:41:19,380 --> 00:41:20,300
Back to the days in Nanxiao,

649
00:41:20,300 --> 00:41:22,180
he was well-versed in both literature and martial arts.

650
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:23,340
He once tamed

651
00:41:23,340 --> 00:41:25,420
a running battle steed with just one hand.

652
00:41:25,420 --> 00:41:28,060
His martial arts skills are much better than yours.

653
00:41:28,060 --> 00:41:30,780
It's already in the past, not worth mentioning.

654
00:41:32,500 --> 00:41:34,960
In that case, I wanna compete with you again.

655
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:39,580
I surrender.

656
00:41:40,020 --> 00:41:41,740
Surrender or not, you can't say that

657
00:41:41,740 --> 00:41:43,340
until we have a competition.

658
00:41:51,060 --> 00:41:52,180
This disciple of mine

659
00:41:52,180 --> 00:41:53,580
once stayed half a month

660
00:41:53,860 --> 00:41:56,120
along the riverside to learn how to swim.

661
00:41:56,300 --> 00:41:58,100
You don't have much going on right now anyway.

662
00:41:58,100 --> 00:41:59,140
It's not a bad idea

663
00:41:59,340 --> 00:42:00,700
to practice a little after chanting sutras.

